sequenceDiagram
    participant Hub as Hub Control Plane
    participant Policy as Policy Decision Point
    participant Queue as Hub Task Queue
    participant Worker as Delegated Worker
    participant Verify as Verification Service
    participant Artifact as Artifact Store
    participant Audit as Audit Log

    Hub->>Policy: Evaluate routing + security policy
    Policy-->>Hub: Permit + explainability metadata
    Hub->>Queue: Enqueue delegated task
    Queue->>Worker: Deliver execution request
    Worker-->>Hub: Execution result + trace evidence
    Hub->>Verify: Run verification checks
    Verify-->>Hub: Verification decision + evidence
    Hub->>Artifact: Publish user summary + detailed artifact
    Hub->>Audit: Append routing/verification/audit events
